{"word":"G4301 - προλαμβάνω - prolambánō - prol-am-ban'-o - Come aforehand","slug":"G4301","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προλαμβάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>prolambánō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>prol-am-ban'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Come aforehand"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03BB;&#x03B1;&#x03BC;&#x03B2;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9; - prolambano&#x0304;</b> - <i>prol-am-ban'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G2983\">G2983</a>; to <i>take in advance</i>, that is, (literally) <i>eat before</i> others have an opportunity; (figuratively) to <i>anticipate</i>, <i>surprise:</i> - come aforehand, overtake, take before."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1949\">G1949</a>, <a href=\"#/G2638\">G2638</a>, <a href=\"#/G2983\">G2983</a>, <a href=\"#/G3335\">G3335</a>, <a href=\"#/G3336\">G3336</a>, <a href=\"#/G353\">G353</a>, <a href=\"#/G354\">G354</a>, <a href=\"#/G3880\">G3880</a>, <a href=\"#/G423\">G423</a>, <a href=\"#/G4355\">G4355</a>, <a href=\"#/G4356\">G4356</a>, <a href=\"#/G5274\">G5274</a>"}]}